<messaging:emailTemplate subject="PO  {!RelatedTo.ASI_MFM_Supplier_Name__r.name}    PO {!RelatedTo.Name} - PR {!RelatedTo.ASI_MFM_Purchase_Request__r.name}           " recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_MFM_PO__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>   <table>     <tr><td> 구매팀 입니다. </td> </tr>            <tr><td> 요청하신 PR에 대해 첨부와 같이 거래처에 PO를 발송 하오니,</td> </tr>        <tr><td> 신청 내용과 일치하는지 확인 하시기 바랍니다.  </td> </tr>         <tr><td> PO번호가 적시되어 있는지 확인 하시기 바랍니다.  </td> </tr>         <tr><td> 진행절차 </td> </tr>         <tr><td> 1.     구매팀에서 구매오더[PO] 발행 여부를 이메일로 수신하여 확인,  </td> </tr>         <tr><td>2.     Agency로부터 재화와 용역의 입고를 확인한 후에 Agency로부터 세금계산서 및 거래명세표 접수, </td> </tr>        <tr><td>3.     Agency로부터 세금계산서 및 거래명세표 접수한 후 MFM에서 입고(Receipt) 처리,  </td> </tr>       <tr><td> 4.     입고(Receipt) 처리를 한 이후에 MFM에서 Expense Claim Form 작성. </td> </tr>            <tr><td> &nbsp;</td></tr>   </table><table><tr><td> This email is to inform you about PO creation from Purchasing team.</td> </tr>            <tr><td> We are about to send PO details to the vendor based on your purchase request.</td> </tr>        <tr><td> Kindly review the details of PO and confirm if the order is correctly placed. </td> </tr>         <tr><td> Please make sure that PO number is written on the packing list or tax invoice when you receive </td> </tr>         <tr><td> the packing list and the tax invoice from agency or supplier.</td> </tr>  <tr><td> &nbsp;</td></tr>        <tr><td> PO Procedure </td> </tr>         <tr><td>1. Receive emails about PO creation from purchasing team </td> </tr>        <tr><td>2. When shipment is delivered or service is rendered, and receive tax invoices from supplier.</td> </tr>       <tr><td> 3. Proceed PO receipt in MFM </td> </tr>         <tr><td> 4. Proceed Payment request creation and approval in MFM </td> </tr>     <tr><td> &nbsp;</td></tr>   </table>  <c:ASI_MFM_KR_POApprovedEmailComp recID="{!RelatedTo.Id}"/> <br/> <c:ASI_MFM_KR_Approver_Comment recID="{!RelatedTo.Id}"/> </body></html></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>